# Keep evals/results/ tracked.
#
# Result files (evals/results/<skill>-<sha>-<date>.md, from TEMPLATE.md) are per-machine:
# they depend on live network/job-board state and the local model version, so they are NOT a
# shared source of truth. They are tracked for now for convenience; a maintainer may add
# `evals/results/*.md` (keeping TEMPLATE.md and this .gitkeep) to .gitignore later.
